<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17283</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西要查出普雷斯托到底想要干什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿，朋友们。”她对朋友们说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我才想起来我要帮我妈妈做一些家务活。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我马上就回来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西在电视台看到了史密斯侦探。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他正在看一些设备。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“普雷斯托在哪儿？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道。”侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我到的时候，他已经走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西笑了。“我很惊讶，大力士居然没有阻止他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈。”史密斯侦探假装笑道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大力士不像你，他可不是真的超级英雄。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得查出普雷斯托在干什么。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，我想……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“救命！”一个声音从门后传来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85201</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西向四周望了望。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那听起来像是……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90973</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大力士！”史密斯侦探说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90974</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跑到门口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门被锁上了。嗞轰！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西用眼睛里射出的激光把门炸开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大力士和节目工作人员都被关在了里面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你，火箭女孩儿。”大力士说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不客气。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你知道普雷斯托去哪儿了吗？”史密斯侦探问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不知道。”另外一个人回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他偷了一台摄像机，然后就逃跑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是我们有办法知道他在干什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人打开了一台显示器。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普雷斯托出现在了显示器上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他一只手拿着魔杖，另一只手拿着麦克风。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>背景是美罗城银行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普雷斯托向一个女人走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个女人戴着一条钻石项链。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162740</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您好!”普雷斯托说，“请问您的名字是什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162741</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“莫莉。”女人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多好听的名字啊！”普雷斯托说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169800</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来给你表演一场魔术，莫莉！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挥舞着他的魔杖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一，二，三……变！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰！莫莉的项链消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184091</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普雷斯托看着摄像机。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家觉得我的节目好看吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来，普雷斯托走向一个男人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“先生，您好！”普雷斯托说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，您戴着的这块手表看上去很不错。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，谢谢。”男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您喜欢魔术吗？”普雷斯托先生问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看这个。”普雷斯托说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挥舞着他的魔杖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一，二，三……变！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰！手表不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西也不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237805</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她必须阻止普雷斯托继续偷东西！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237806</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探还在看着显示器。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244142</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿，我们需要采取行动了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244143</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普雷斯托他……火箭女孩儿？她去哪里了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>